</strong><br />
<a href="http://godofnumbers.deviantart.com/art/Philippine-Lower-Mythology-Series-1-410029028" data-ga_click_event="{&quot;category&quot;:&quot;Deviation&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;description_title&quot;,&quot;nofollow&quot;:0}">Philippine Lower Mythology Series 1</a> <small><span class="by">by</span> <span class="username-with-symbol u"><a class="u regular username" href="http://godofnumbers.deviantart.com/" data-ga_click_event="{&quot;category&quot;:&quot;Deviation&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;description_author&quot;,&quot;nofollow&quot;:0}">GodOfNumbers</a></span></small></p>
