-widget-link" href="https://www.aswangproject.com/the-manobos-of-agusan-sacrifices-war-rites/">The MANÓBOS of Agusan: Sacrifices &#038; War Rites...</a></div><div class="mashsb-excerpt">The Manobo are several people groups who inhabit the island of Mindanao in the Philippines. They spe</div> <span class="mashicon-share">882 Shares</span></li></ul></aside><!-- MashShare Most Popular Widget End //--><aside id="block-69" class="widget widget_block clearfix"></aside>
